  }, "Know your audience.")), mdx("p", null, "That is the exact name of one of the projects that some of us at Toastmasters have completed. The goal is to find out as much information as possible about your audience \u2014 their age, experience, what PR practices they would need to apply in their clubs, and so on."), mdx("div", {
